<ab facs="#facs_57_r1l38"><expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> <expan>mitburg<ex>er</ex></expan> gar <expan>vngütlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>geſcheh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſeẏ vnd 
<add><ab facs="#facs_57_r1l37">noch </ab></add> geſchehe / Als das </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_57_r1l39"><expan>etlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> ~ mitburgern dıe <expan>frum<ex>m</ex></expan> leute ſein wol küntlich vnd <expan>wiſʒentl<ex>ich</ex></expan> </ab>
