<del rend="strikethrough">daran vnd b </del> doch wie darümb / ſo <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir den <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_57_r1l41"><expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> durch <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> daran gevveiſet / daʒ Er 
