<ab facs="#facs_58_r1l8">v̈mb <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>vveiſh<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>allcʒ<ex>eit</ex></expan> gern <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dienen</expan> / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> vȷ̃ <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Nereẏ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_58_r1l9">et Achılleẏ Anno etc Octauo </ab>
